overview: Stockholm, Sweden is the spot, and you will see the usual suspects doing Trains, Backjumps, Wholecars, Panels, Insides & more of that. The action neavau is high and lots of ill and fresh fatcap styles. Sweden kicks ass again with these: WUFC, SDK, Y2K, MOA, ViM, FUPS, AE, FAME, HiT. Almost 70 minutes of great live actions and rolling trains.
title: Friendly Fire
